      "_id": "c73w2FugGkbE0lSu",
      "name": "Create Whirlwind",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The djinni conjures a whirlwind at a point it can see within 36 m. The whirlwind fills a 6 m-radius, 18 m-high Cylinder centered on that point. The whirlwind lasts until the djinni's Concentration on it ends. The djinni can move the whirlwind up to 6 m at the start of each of its turns.\nWhenever the whirlwind enters uma criatura's space or uma criatura enters the whirlwind, that creature is subjected to the following effect. Teste de Resistência de Força: CD 17 (uma criatura makes this save only once per turn, and the djinni is unaffected). While in the whirlwind, o alvo fica com a condição Impedido and moves with the whirlwind. At the start of each of its turns, the Impedido target takes 21 (6d6) dano trovejante. At the end of each of its turns, o alvo repeats the save, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
